    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but it doesn't feel like self-care is gonna fix it. like the more i try to be me, the more everything just breaks. it feels like i'm just playing a losing game. like there's no version of the future where i actually get to exist without being exhausted or judged. it's just... constant. i'm just so done with the weight of it all.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
